// BP_SodPlayerController — Blueprint subclass of ASodPlayerController
// Location: /Game/Game/Blueprints/Player/BP_SodPlayerController

/*
To create in UE5 Editor:
1. Create new Blueprint extending ASodPlayerController
2. Set default properties:
   - LightWeaver_IMC = IMC_ShardsOfDawn_LightWeaver
   - ShadowWalker_IMC = IMC_ShardsOfDawn_ShadowWalker
   - HUDClass = BP_SodHUD
3. Implement Blueprint events:
   - ShowInteractionPrompt → Create Widget showing E key + text
   - HideInteractionPrompt → Remove Widget
   - ShowArchetypeNotification → Play archetype intro UI
*/
